{
  "stem": "22652.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't know if my parents would ever return.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think we all knew our life could never be, quote, 'normal' again, as if nothing had happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So there was a little apprehension about the future.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But basically, we were very joyful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I must say that-- I must say that the, the social workers and the nuns were very caring and supportive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I-- one story-- Deniz wanted me to tell that story, so I'm going to tell it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She wanted me to tell it to the nuns of Notre Dame de Sureiu.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so, I remember it very vividly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were sitting at the table having a nice lunch and looking out the window.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I noticed that on the window there were some pieces of bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the nuns had saved it for the birds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And when they weren't looking, I stole the pieces of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I ate them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then the nuns and the social worker saying, I swear there was bread on the window.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I wonder what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I didn't see any birds coming and getting the bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I just looked somewhere else and pretended.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I confessed to the nuns 50 years later that-- [LAUGHTER] --I was the one that stole the bread from the birds.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always have dreams about bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just also want to mention-- [LAUGHS] [POINTING] I was put in with peasants after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were separated, the three of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the woman used to make very good soup, you know, nice, creamy soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by that time, we were liberated, so there was plenty food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so when the soup was left in the pot, she would say to me, give, give the left over to the cat.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
